Test for issue #3661: adding stored attribute to columnar table without docstore

Bug: ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN on columnar table with no stored fields/attrs tried to rename missing .spds and corrupted table.
Fix: correctly count stored attrs in new schema so docstore file juggling only happens when needed.

